page.title: 20POPULATION
page.content:
LYNEAL VILLAGE: is a quiet village reached only by narrow lanes. Its inhabitants are varied in occupation(there are 2 small rows of council houses) but it has quite a high proportion of retired people and many of its inhabitants are elderly.There is no industry or employment in the village.
THESE 20 TEXT PAGES WERE WRITTEN BY: Asha Qureshi 8 Christine Lewis 8 Lisa Morris 8 Emma Kay 8 Adam Williams 8 Patrick Wickson 8 Emma Howard 9 Suzanne Forrester 9 Christy Vermeulen 9 Sonrisa Hipkins 9 Michelle Evans 9 Darren Thompstone 10 Christopher Panting 10 Sylvia Lewis 10 Helen Marshall 11 Angela Farmer 11
